message.body: No that's cool. You can hold onto them. Thanks. We will have to leave again tomorrow at 830. Will you plan to be here at 8 again? Just let us know. Thanks
Yeah I can be there at 8
Even if it's closer To 830 that would be fine too. We just have to put all animals away. Thanks
Hi hunter. We are going to leave a little early but you can let yourself in right? The animals will be away and the basement door us unlocked if you need to get in there again. Thanks.
